    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape for its next owner! It drives smoothly, the interior is super comfy, and it's been well-loved. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Feel free to shoot me a message\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
