    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 987.1 Cayman S is a precision-engineered mid-engine masterpiece featuring the 3.4L flat-six M97.21 powerplant. The engine exhibits excellent compression and a clean valvetrain, paired with a 6-speed manual transaxle that offers short, tactile throws. The chassis benefits from Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), ensuring optimal damping characteristics during high-lateral-G maneuvers. Recent maintenance includes a cooling system overhaul with a new water pump and a comprehensive brake service using high-boiling-point fluid. The hydraulic steering rack provides communicative feedback, and the factory-tuned exhaust note remains crisp. A mechanically sound example ready for the technical demands of the track or spirited canyon carving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
