    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman in classic Guards Red. This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity to own a mid-engined masterpiece that has been maintained with an open checkbook. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; the turbocharged engine delivers consistent power, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. The interior features premium black leather that has been regularly conditioned, showing only minimal softening on the driver's side bolster. All electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Externally, the car presents beautifully with a deep, mirror-like finish. To be fully transparent, there are light stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side alloy wheel, typical of careful road use. It comes with a complete service log, two keys, and tires with plenty of life left. This is a turn-key performance car that balances daily usability with weekend thrills.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
