    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and it\u2019s honestly such a solid, reliable ride. It\u2019s been well-loved and is still in great shape, perfect for zipping around town or hitting the highway for a weekend getaway! I've kept up with the maintenance, and it runs like a charm. If you're looking for something dependable that still looks awesome on the road, this is the one for you. I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have, so feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019m super happy to chat!",
      "price": 29900.0,
