      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS high-pressure variable valve timing system. Power is sent to the rear wheels through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. To ensure chassis longevity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with MacPherson struts and multi-link rear architecture. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and inspection of the rod bearings, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates within tight tolerances. A true driver's car with the mechanical pedigree to match.",
